name: Quantum Stone Hercule
description:
Last NFT of the serie of monumental
statues in natural environment. An
animation based on one of the real
marble statues of the artist Leo
Caillard. This statue is inspired by the
iconic ? Hercule Farnese ? from
ancient Greece. Leo Caillard carves
marble with distorsions to create a
new version of the ancient statue. In
between "Reality" of the Stone and
"Virtuality" of the shape. If the price of
this NFT reaches 8 eth, the buyer will
be allowed to claim a real and unique
marble version of this statue made by
Leo Caillard.
